<h1>Influence Mapping February Roundup</h1>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Welcome again to our monthly roundup with stories around transparency and accountability, along with investigative journalism, studies and tools for the data practitioners. </span></p>
<p class="p1">Share your thoughts, needs, achievements and failures in our <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/influencemapping" target="_blank">Google Group</a>, hear about Influence Mapping projects in <a href="http://influencemapping.org/blog/" target="_blank">our Blog</a> and <a href="https://public.etherpad-mozilla.org/p/im-sciencefair-14-10-15" target="_blank">join our Science Fair</a>!<!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form --></p>

